-- E-Ton Solar Rises to Almost Four-Month High After Announcing Bond Plan
-- B y   A d e l a   L i n
-- 2010-12-24T01:18:47Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-12-24/e-ton-solar-rises-to-almost-four-month-high-after-announcing-bond-plan.html
E-Ton Solar Tech Co. jumped to the
highest in nearly four months in Taipei trading after announcing
a plan to sell up to NT$6 billion of convertible bonds.  The stock advanced 2.8 percent to NT$46.00 as of 9:07 a.m.,
the highest since Aug. 27. It also plans to sell as many as
300 million shares to help repay debt and fund the purchase of
equipment and raw material, the Tainan, Taiwan-based company
said in a statement yesterday.   To contact the reporter on this story:
Adela Lin in Taipei at 
